OL,3,CGuernsey motorcyclists required to
OL,4,Ctake theory test for first time
OL,6,FMotorcyclists in with a provisional
OL,7,Flicence will now have to pass a formal
OL,8,Fcomputer-based theory test before they
OL,9,Fcan start practical training to be
OL,10,Fallowed to ride unsupervised on the
OL,11,Fisland's roads.
OL,13,FIt will cost #50 to take and includes
OL,14,Fquestions on hazards which officials
OL,15,Fsay will make local roads safer.
OL,17,FHowever, there are concerns from some
OL,18,Fthat riders will struggle to adapt.
