OL,3,CGuernsey motorcyclists required to
OL,4,Ctake theory test for first time
OL,6,FAdvanced Training Instructor Tom
OL,7,FBurnett explains: "The difficulty as I
OL,8,Fsee it is there aren't many children
OL,9,Faged 14, 15 or 16 years old who will
OL,10,Fput in the study that's required and
OL,11,Fsuccessfully complete the theory test.
OL,13,F"It's difficult enough for adults. I
OL,14,Fdid a theory test recently and it
OL,15,Fcertainly wasn't easy."
OL,17,FMotorcyclist Owen Stanley says he
OL,18,Fwould have thought twice about getting
OL,19,Fa bike if he had to do the extra
OL,20,Ftraining.
