OL,3,CGuernsey motorcyclists required to
OL,4,Ctake theory test for first time
OL,6,FHe explains: "I got handed a piece of
OL,7,Fpaper with 20 questions. I had to get
OL,8,Fmore than 15 right, otherwise I'd fail
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,F"I ended up getting 16 and I wouldn't
OL,12,Fwant to get a bike if I had to be sat
OL,13,Fdoing 50 questions on a computer just
OL,14,Ffor that."
OL,16,FYoung people can ride a 50cc motorbike
OL,17,Ffrom the age of 14 in Guernsey, lower
OL,18,Fthan the UK where someone needs to be
OL,19,Fat least 16.
