OL,3,CGuernsey motorcyclists required to
OL,4,Ctake theory test for first time
OL,6,FClinton Millard co-owns a motorbike
OL,7,Fshop and says no matter what rules are
OL,8,Fin place, risk comes down to
OL,9,Findividual responsibility.
OL,11,FHe adds: "You will always get groups
OL,12,Fof children who will ride probably not
OL,13,Fso safely and I don't think that's
OL,14,Fsomething we can really change by
OL,15,Fputting a test at the start.
OL,17,F"It's going to set everyone up for
OL,18,Fsuccess, but it really is down to the
OL,19,Findividual road user as to how they
OL,20,Fride."
